column5: Hey, well I was going to keep this quiet but fish-miester and I caught nothing this evening on Scugog. Now giving up on it but I would like to get some info on Sturgeon Lake  I am looking for the nearest park or boat ramp where we can park and walk out onto the Ice to fish(Closest from Lindsay). If somebody can give me a name of a park or place to go that would be great!  Thanks, MTBF
snug harbour marine. google it. a good place to fish the south end
If you mean the Moorings, It is now marked Private Property, no access except to members and guests. Mike, Check your PM, I won't post a public access point openly on the board.
PM Checked, thanks for the info Cliff
